import { Component, OnInit, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { DOCUMENT } from '@angular/common'; import { Router, ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-aboutus', templateUrl: './aboutus.component.html', styleUrls: ['./aboutus.component.css'] }) export class AboutusComponent implements OnInit { constructor( @Inject(DOCUMENT) private document: Document, private router: Router, private route: ActivatedRoute ) {} ngOnInit() { this.scrollToTop(); } scrollToTop() { this.document.body.scrollTop = 0; this.document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0; } showArchitecture() { this.router.navigate(['architecture']); } }

WE HAVE 3 YEARS OF EXPERIENCE IN THIS FIELD.

_______

With three years of dedicated experience, HPSV Studio has established itself as a proficient player in the field of architecture and design. Our expertise extends to planning layouts and constructing buildings for prestigious entities like the Pune Corporation, PMRDA, and related offices. Across diverse projects, including public buildings, schools, commercial complexes, residential spaces, bungalows, industrial sheds, corporate offices, and banks, we showcase our versatility in Architecture, Interior Design, and Liasoning. Our commitment to delivering innovative and tailored solutions remains unwavering, ensuring the success of each project we undertake.

Architecture

When the design concepts have been decided, the architect prepares working drawings and specifications.

Interior

You may engage your architect to provide an interior service, advising on loose furniture.

Liasoning

As one of the successful architecture firms, we also play a pivotal role when it comes to Liasoning services.
